{
  "stem": "5328.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But just at school we spoke the Hebrew language.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At home we spoke Yiddish-- and Polish, eventually.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But mainly Yiddish at home we spoke.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it's been the same.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's just the language is in Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had all-- we had geometry, we had geography, we had language, and everything.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But, instead of being in Polish, it was in Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was in Hashomer Hatzair as a child.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we used to get together a specific place and associate with each other.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Mind you, I was still a little girl when the time-- was until 1941.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was still young.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I remember the Hebrew organization-- I mean the Hashomer Hatzair.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We associated.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they-- Friday night and Saturday mornings.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because in Poland we didn't have, like, the weekends-- Saturday and Sunday off.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had school.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We didn't go to school on Saturday, but we went on Sunday.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The Polish people didn't go on Sunday to school, but they did go on Saturday to school.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So this was the difference between the Jews and the Pole, because in the wintertime where we went on Sunday to school, and they went to church.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we got some snowballs they were throwing at us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because they knew that this is Jewish children.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, there was a lot, even.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was written on the poles 'Zydzi do Palestyny.' That means 'Jews, go to Palestine.' And 'we hate Jews.' It was written all over.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, he had no problem.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No problem.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I really don't know why.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But-- well, to tell the truth, everywhere and anywhere it was the anti-Semitism there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some showed it more, some showed it less.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the anti-Semitism was there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had an older sister.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was Shulamid Zucker.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
